# The academic classic: 12-month momentum skipping the most recent month
# (the skip dodges short-term reversal). A trend gate keeps names below
# their 200-day out of the book entirely, weights lean toward the calmer
# names, and no single position may exceed a quarter of the portfolio.

strategy "Twelve Minus One"

universe [sp_top_30]
rebalance monthly

hold top 5 by [momentum 252 skip=21]
  where price above [sma 200]
  weighted by [inverse_volatility 20]

risk [max_position 25%]
